
To explore Ethernet IPs for SBiG:

1) Find the IP address by using NetBIOS service via CMD:
nbtstat.exe -a GEMINI
nbtstat.exe -c
Then find the correspondance GEMINI with IP
 
2) Establish UDP connection to IP port 11110

# --- TCL code
package require udp
set udpSock [udp_open]
udp_conf $udpSock $ip 11110
fconfigure $udpSock -buffering none -translation binary
set compteur 0
flush $udpSock
